      "title": "Nationwide curfew!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The curfew has been enforced from 12 pm today to 5 am tomorrow (14).",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe announced this announcement through a special gazette.",
        "It is noteworthy that no information has been released specifically regarding the curfew enforced in the Upper Province."
